title: ApeCoin DAO
content: The ApeCoin community governs itself via the ApeCoin DAO, the decentralized governance framework that supports the Ecosystem Fund. The DAO follows a proposal process to vote on how the Ecosystem Fund will be distributed by the APE Foundation to promote a diverse and self-sustaining ecosystem. This governance guide is an overview of the proposal process. It’s a living document that will evolve and improve with the DAO community’s input.
